curl -O https://hyperledger.github.io/composer/latest/prereqs-ubuntu.sh

chmod u+x prereqs-ubuntu.sh

./prereqs-ubuntu.sh


Refer this:
https://hyperledger.github.io/composer/latest/installing/development-tools

########
If any docker related issue arises, type following command..

sudo usermod -a -G docker $USER

Run this command in your favourite shell and then completely log out of your account and log back in 
